# Gas City
.gc/
.beads/
hooks/
.runtime/

# Beads / Dolt files (added by bd init)
.dolt/
*.db
.beads-credential-key
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/ralph-loop.local.md

# gc-managed artifacts regenerated on every `gc start`:
# - formulas/* listed below are re-seeded from the embedded `core` pack by
#   writeInitFormulas (cmd/gc/init_artifacts.go) when absent.
# - scripts/* are symlinks rebuilt by resolveConfiguredScripts
#   (cmd/gc/city_runtime.go) pointing into .gc/system/packs/*/scripts/.
# Tracking them would just churn on every gc binary upgrade.
formulas/mol-do-work.toml
formulas/mol-polecat-base.toml
formulas/mol-polecat-commit.toml
formulas/mol-scoped-work.toml
scripts/
